# Production build settings (read by Vite during `npm run build`).
# The optional "Ask the Specs" Cloudflare Worker. This is a public endpoint (the browser
# calls it directly), not a secret — safe to commit. Without it, Ask falls back to keyword
# search. See worker/ and DEPLOY.md.
VITE_ASK_URL=https://wsdot-ask-the-specs.jacihayden.workers.dev
